      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NO MORE TROUBLE (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Bulli in a handy 22.67 beating Fantasia Queen. Has a win and two minor placings from three starts from this draw. Sure to prove hard to beat. SAMMY MY BOY (1) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 5th at this track in NG company. Has a good record here at this journey. Expected to give a good account. FLORIDA LINE (7) was below best last time finishing fourth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at this track. Can turn it around this time. CRIMSON DYNAMO (6) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
